    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Lots of Cats in Every Moment” is a game where you find hidden cats while romance unfolds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl ends up raising a kitten after an unexpected event. What will occur because of this? Find the cats hidden in the beautiful and diverse hand-drawn landscapes and listen to their story, meow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Over 1800 Cats and Special Items!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Part 1 (free): 5+1 main landscapes, 5 interactable comic strips, 650+ cats, 250 items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Part 2 (DLC): 5+1 main landscapes, 5 interactable comic strips, 650+ cats, 250 items</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All comic strips and main landscapes are connected through story progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hints can be used once per minute.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No penalty for clicking on a spot without a cat. Search freely.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Has an original soundtrack, with unique tracks featured in each episode. Another BGM set is also available, so you can choose the one that you like best.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every illustration is 100% hand-drawn and crafted with love.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080240/extras/995136d2ebf0ad3b39cd8dc7ee76b71b.poster.avif?t=1768413387\" width=580 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080240/extras/995136d2ebf0ad3b39cd8dc7ee76b71b.webm?t=1768413387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\